@startuml
[Frontend Web Interface] as frontend
[API Gateway] as api_gateway
[Feature Extraction Service] as feature_service
[URLNet Model Service] as urlnet_service
[Transformer Model Service] as transformer_service
[Database Service] as db_service
[Model Training Service] as training_service

frontend --> api_gateway : HTTP Requests
api_gateway --> feature_service : Feature extraction requests
api_gateway --> urlnet_service : URLNet processing requests
api_gateway --> transformer_service : Transformer processing requests
feature_service --> db_service : Store features
urlnet_service --> db_service : Store predictions
transformer_service --> db_service : Store predictions
api_gateway --> db_service : Retrieve results
training_service --> db_service : Access training data
training_service --> urlnet_service : Update URLNet model
training_service --> transformer_service : Update Transformer model

note right of frontend
  React/Vue.js based
  user interface
end note

note right of api_gateway
  FastAPI/Flask
  REST API
end note

note right of feature_service
  Python-based feature
  extraction module
end note

note right of urlnet_service
  PyTorch-based CNN
  model for URL analysis
end note

note right of transformer_service
  PyTorch-based Transformer
  model for URL analysis
end note

note right of db_service
  SQLite/PostgreSQL
  for data storage
end note

note right of training_service
  Model training and
  evaluation pipeline
end note
@enduml